I'm confused, okay?

964
01:19:29,694 --> 01:19:31,487
Even your friend Sean
asked about...

965
01:19:31,654 --> 01:19:33,739
He's not my friend, if you didn't know.

966
01:19:33,906 --> 01:19:38,578
He asked me about you.
What time you came home.

967
01:19:39,245 --> 01:19:42,582
- What'd you tell him?
- I said I was asleep.

968
01:19:43,541 --> 01:19:46,669
- That's good thinking, baby.
- Jesus Christ, Dave!

969
01:19:46,836 --> 01:19:49,755
- Why not tell them about the mugger?
- The mugger?

970
01:19:49,922 --> 01:19:52,550
The mugger! I see how
your mind's working. I do.

971
01:19:52,717 --> 01:19:55,928
I come home with blood on me
the same night Katie's murdered.

972
01:19:56,095 --> 01:19:57,763
